					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5191949#post-3704239</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5191949/scp-3403#post-3704239</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2018 02:04:28 +0000</pubDate>
								<wikidot:authorUserId>3486621</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I really like this one. You helped me a lot with my writing and I think yours is excellent. This SCP tugs at my heartstrings a little and reminds me of when I buried my cremated cat. It balances sad and creepy together very well with the test logs and the overall questions about its origins. The flower is also a very nice, sweet little touch and helps counterbalance the more gruesome later imagery. All in all, a nice heartstring-tugger.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
